<h2 id="departmental-board">Departmental Board</h2>

<p>The Departmental Board provides direction on strategy, performance and risk management.</p>

<h3 id="members">Members</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/greg-clark">The Rt Hon Greg Clark MP</a>, Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (Chair)</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/claire-perry">The Rt Hon Claire Perry MP</a>, Minister of State for Energy and Clean Growth</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/archie-norman">Archie Norman</a>, Lead Non-Executive Board Member (Deputy Chair)</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/leena-nair">Leena Nair</a>, Non-Executive Board Member and Chair of the <a href="#nominations-and-governance-committee">Nominations and Governance Committee</a>
</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/carolyn-mccall">Dame Carolyn McCall</a>, Non-Executive Board Member</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nigel-boardman">Nigel Boardman</a>, Non-Executive Board Member and Chair of the <a href="#audit-risk-and-assurance-committee">Audit and Risk Assurance Committee</a>
</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/kathryn-parsons">Kathryn Parsons</a>, Non-Executive Board Member</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/stephen-a-carter">Stephen Carter</a>, Non-Executive Board Member</li>
  <li>
